		 For any inquiries.
		</h1>
		
		<div class="flex space-x-4">
			<div class="bg-blue-700 bg-opacity-30 border-2 border-blue-700 shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 w-1/2">
			  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-blue-500 to-blue-400 inline-block text-transparent bg-clip-text mb-4">Discord</h2>
			  <p class="text-gray-100">
				<a href="discord:paxzdev" class="hover:underline font-bold">@paxzdev</a>
			  </p>
			  <p class="text-gray-200">Click the link to open your Discord client.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 w-1/2">
			  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-blue-500 to-blue-400 inline-block text-transparent bg-clip-text mb-4">
				Email</h2>
			  <p class="text-gray-600">
				<a href="mailto:paxzgotbanned123@g" class="hover:underline font-bold">paxzgotbanned123@gmail.com</a>
			  </p>
			  <p class="text-gray-600">
				Click the link to open your email client and send a message.
			  </p>
			</div>
		  </div>

		
		
	  </div>
	</main>

	<footer class="bg-gray-100">
